  "synopsis": "The story of the Hand Island no Bouken special is set a little before the events of One Piece Film Z and depicts a major \"Hand Island\" incident during the New World storyline. The story is set at \"Cannon Town\" where a parent and a child work as craftspeople. The incident revolves around them and a commodore of a marine base. The special will also have a flashback scene to the story in the first chapter of the manga, but with new animation. \n\n(Source: ANN)",
